snippet.title: Heartland: Amber & Graham answer fan questions from Facebook & Twitter | Heartland | CBC
snippet.description:
Heartland stars Amber Marshall and Graham Wardle answer fan questions about Amy and Ty's wedding, Chris Potter, motorcycles and stunt riding on horses.
Subscribe: http://bit.ly/CBCSubscribe
Watch Full Episodes of Heartland: http://bit.ly/FullEpisodesCBC 

About Heartland: Heartland is a family drama on CBC TV about a family dealing with the highs and lows of life on a horse ranch in the stunning the foothills of Alberta.
